# Minimal Change Discipline

- Prefer the smallest safe implementation that satisfies the requirement.
- Avoid unnecessary refactors and avoid touching unrelated files.
- Do not rewrite stable code without explicit request.
- Reuse or extend existing implementation before introducing new patterns.
- If an existing implementation already satisfies the requirement, do not rewrite it.
